<!-- How It Works -->
<section class="py-6">
    <div class="row justify-content-center mb-7 px-7">
        <div class="col-12 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-primary">How It Works</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 text-center steps-list-ctnr mb-4">
            <div class="row steps-list">
                <div class="col-xl-4 steps-item" data-aos="fade-right">
                    <div class="steps-steps-number-wrap">
                        <div class="steps-number text-secondary">1</div>
                        <div class="steps-cover-wrap">
                            <div class="steps-cover"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="content">
                        <div class="icon text-primary"><i class="fa-regular fa-lightbulb"></i></div>
                        <h2 class="text-secondary">Discover</h2>
                        <p>Start by telling us a bit about yourself. This might include your current interests, past hobbies, and how much free time you have..</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xl-4 steps-item" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <div class="steps-steps-number-wrap">
                        <div class="steps-number text-secondary">2</div>
                        <div class="steps-cover-wrap">
                            <div class="steps-cover"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="content">
                        <div class="icon text-primary"><i class="fa-regular fa-map"></i></div>
                        <h2 class="text-secondary">Explore</h2>
                        <p>Use our unique hobby discovery tool to explore a wide range of activities. You can swipe right if you're interested, or swipe left to pass. Our smart algorithm learns from your choices to recommend hobbies that are more likely to suit your preferences.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xl-4 steps-item" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="400">
                    <div class="steps-steps-number-wrap">
                        <div class="steps-number text-secondary">3</div>
                        <div class="steps-cover-wrap">
                            <div class="steps-cover"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="content">
                        <div class="icon iconAirplane text-primary"><i class="fa-solid fa-flask"></i></div>
                        <h2 class="text-secondary">Immerse</h2>
                        <p>Once you've swiped right on a hobby, you'll get access to a wealth of information. This includes tutorial videos, beginner's guides, and user reviews to help you get started.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>                
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<!-- End How It Works -->

